    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s been super well-loved? I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and honestly, it\u2019s still running like a dream! It\u2019s in great shape and has plenty of life left for all your upcoming road trips or daily commutes. It\u2019s been kept clean and tidy, and I think you\u2019re really going to love how it handles on the road. Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
      "price": 34500.0,
