    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle strikes the perfect balance between luxury and utility, presenting in well-cared-for condition. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, though a close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips and light surface scratches consistent with careful road use. Inside, the cabin is a smoke-free environment with well-preserved upholstery that shows only mild creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster. All electronics, including the dual-zone climate control and premium sound system, function perfectly. Mechanically, the car is very sound; it has been maintained with regular oil changes and inspections, resulting in a smooth, quiet ride and a responsive transmission. It is a reliable, honest car that is ready for its next owner without any immediate maintenance needs.",
      "price": 34500.0,
