    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. This high-revving naturally aspirated engine utilizes individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing to deliver a linear power band up to an 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M-Differential lock for optimal torque distribution. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive subframe reinforcement and a VANOS bulletproofing kit. The suspension geometry remains precise with refreshed bushings and calibrated dampers, ensuring the chassis handles high lateral G-loads with composure. While the exterior shows minor signs of spirited use, the mechanical synchronicity and powertrain response remain exceptional.",
